#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introducción"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmix; supports several platforms and sound drivers."
msgstr "&kmix; admite varias plataformas y controladores de sonido."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr ""
"Si tiene instalados los controladores ALSA y Open Sound System, &kmix; "
"utilizará el controlador ALSA."

